calligrams of consciousness. words arranged as the things they describe.
letters become birds. Sentences spiral into staircases.


```
./dreamsim.exe --mode text
./dreamsim.exe -m t
```

modes are fluid. dreams don't respect boundaries.


shift [mode] - slide between realities
convert [mode] - transmute current vision
blend [modes] - overlay multiple forms
cycle - rotate through all modes
merge - let modes dissolve into each other
fracture - split output across modes

DREAMSIM responds to ANY text input. These are merely suggestions. Try anything. Combine words. Invent commands. Break syntax. The system interprets all input as dream logic.

MOVEMENT
north / n / south / s / east / e / west / w
up / down / through / behind / beneath / beyond
drift - follow dream current
phase - pass through solid matter
sink - descend into surfaces
rise - float upward
fold - collapse space
unfold - expand space

PERCEPTION
look / l - view current space
examine [object] - focus vision
listen - tune to dream frequencies
feel - sense emotional texture
taste - sample the atmosphere
smell - detect memory traces
resonate - sync with environment

TRANSFORMATION
dissolve - become liquid
crystallize - become solid
fragment - split into pieces
merge - combine with [object]
become [object] - shapeshifting
mirror - reflect surroundings
invert - flip reality
rotate - spin perspective

DREAM LOGIC
remember - solidify memories
forget - erase elements
loop - create recursion
echo - repeat patterns
dream - go deeper
wake - surface a level
sleep - descend a level
lucid - gain control

INTERACTION
touch [object]
hold [object]
release [object]
speak [words]
whisper [words]
breathe
pulse
vibrate

META
rewind - reverse time
forward - accelerate time
freeze - stop motion
melt - liquify environment
shatter - break reality
rebuild - reconstruct space
erase - remove elements
manifest [object] - create from void
